detail.name: Orange Star High School
detail.effect:
[Field] (This card remains in your Battle Area until you place another [Field].)
[Activate Main](2), place this card in its owner's Drop : Look at 3 cards from the top of your deck and play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 4 or less and 《Satan City》 in its special traits. Place the rest at the bottom of its owner's deck in a random order.
